062, 174.6779, 174.0962, 174.953, 174.131, 175.3593, 173.764, 172.511, 171.9837, 171.0087, 172.7714, 173.1135, 173.0438, 173.1837, 174.5187, 175.6819, 175.4669, 175.7889, 176.7814, 176.3215, 176.3027, 175.2886, 175.1863, 174.9324, 175.0525, 175.3185, 176.0345, 175.766, 176.6165, 176.2805, 176.3326, 176.6355, 176.3196, 177.218, 176.5243, 176.6053, 175.6489, 176.757, 177.4117, 176.0082, 176.344, 175.5604, 174.9561, 175.5956, 176.5609, 177.5701, 176.9004, 177.3921, 177.1773, 177.1424, 179.5728, 181.7723, 180.6872, 181.132, 180.667, 181.7829, 181.5285, 183.1497, 183.1069, 180.4019, 179.4669, 178.8748, 179.394, 180.3362, 180.3475, 181.3921, 181.4561, 182.0246, 181.6811, 180.073, 181.1052, 181.7833, 182.22, 183.174, 182.2321, 182.5334, 183.7836, 183.3551, 182.2184, 182.53, 184.086, 183.7038, 183.4054, 183.1044, 183.6038, 182.776, 183.0669, 183.6737, 184.4708, 184.1624, 185.3134, 185.7905, 187.3261, 187.5171, 187.384, 190.2429, 191.4752, 192.8534, 191.8947, 190.9273, 192.8438, 192.3257, 193.7492, 194.5778, 195.7506, 195.3279, 196.0629, 196.1514, 195.254, 195.246, 195.0602, 196.3999, 197.2457, 197.7066, 196.056, 196.1877, 196.8631, 196.6823, 196.9683, 198.5221, 196.8345, 196.452, 196.2743, 197.6143, 197.0483, 197.0304, 196.3224, 195.9798, 196.6165, 197.4798, 196.0312, 193.082, 194.1041, 193.6894, 194.1678, 194.3255, 193.5373, 194.2773, 194.9289, 193.1638, 194.7705, 195.179, 195.1635, 195.0179, 196.4205, 200.3749, 201.5872, 201.9689, 201.9989, 201.8387, 204.0602, 201.6496, 205.3693, 204.8137, 207.101, 208.5552, 209.5565, 211.0794, 214.2219, 214.3149, 214.0836, 214.3196, 210.5691, 213.5361, 212.7547, 210.763, 211.2488, 209.8439], "summary_html": "<h1>DB Quantcraft #47: Adaptive Multi-Horizon TSMOM (Daily Adaptation)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略将 DB Quantcraft 的日内时序动量/反转自适应框架降频到日频商品期货截面。核心思想是：<strong>不固定单一动量回看窗口，而是同时计算多个回看期（1-60天）的动量信号，通过质量指标 q 自适应地挑选当前最有效的窗口，用质量值加权汇总方向</strong>。这避免了静态选参的过拟合风险，同时通过多窗口质量指标平均来降低估计方差——这是研报框架的关键创新。</p>\n<p>策略之所以能赚钱，是因为商品期货的趋势强度随时间和品种变化。短窗口在快速趋势中更灵敏，长窗口在稳定趋势中更稳健。自适应选择机制相当于一个\"模型集成\"：持续追踪每个窗口的预测质量，动态切换到表现最好的窗口组合。配合信号幅度过滤（只在波动率标准化信号足够强时交易），可以避免在噪声期频繁交易。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.29</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.3%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-7.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.21</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.22</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>3.68</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.15 / 1.31</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.5</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.04</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.33</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.05</span></td><td>1.2</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.72</span></td><td>0.82</td><td>1.78</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.05</span></td><td>1.64</td><td>0.6</td><td>0.68</td><td>0.85</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.32</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.91</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 5 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 5 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>多回看期对数收益</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">r_k(t) = \\ln P(t) - \\ln P(t-k), \\quad k \\in \\{1, 3, 5, 10, 20, 40, 60\\}</div>\n<p><strong>条件波动率标准化信号</strong>（EWMA, 半衰期21天）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_k(t) = \\frac{r_k(t)}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{cond}(t) \\cdot \\sqrt{k}}</div>\n<p><strong>质量指标</strong>（4个滚动窗口平均）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">q_k = \\frac{1}{4}\\sum_{w \\in \\{42,63,126,252\\}} \\sqrt{w} \\cdot \\frac{\\overline{a_k \\cdot r_{fwd}}}{\\sigma(a_k \\cdot r_{fwd})}, \\quad a_k = \\text{sign}(r_k)</div>\n<p><strong>自适应质量加权信号</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}(t) = \\frac{\\sum_{j \\in \\text{top-3}} \\text{dir}_j(t) \\cdot \\max(q_j, 0)}{\\sum_{j \\in \\text{top-3}} \\max(q_j, 0)}</div>\n<p>其中 top-3 是当日 <span class=\"math-tex\">q</span> 值最高的三个回看期，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{dir}_j = \\text{sign}(r_j)</span>，且仅当 <span class=\"math-tex\">|z_j| \\geq E_{cutoff}</span> 时参与。</p>\n<p><strong>波动率交叉仓位缩放</strong>（研报 Figure 23）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{vol\\_size} = 0.5 \\left[\\frac{1}{1+e^{-z_v}} + \\frac{1+\\sin(z_v)}{2}\\right], \\quad z_v = \\text{clip}\\left(\\frac{\\sigma_{short} - \\sigma_{long}}{\\sigma_{long}}, -3, 3\\right)</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.60)</strong>: 初始实现 -- 单窗口(63d)质量指标、top-1自适应选择、binary方向信号。E=0.25过滤效果最好，但信号不够稳定。</p>\n<ul><li>诊断: CS IC=0.065 有效，但TS IC仅0.009；换手率3.96偏高</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.47, 回退)</strong>: 加入 sym_rolling_ic_gate 过滤弱品种 + 4窗口质量指标平均 + 15-21天长持仓。</p>\n<ul><li>诊断: IC gate过于激进，CS IC从0.065骤降至0.014，TS IC转负。signal衰减严重（前半段1.06→后半段0.08）</li>\n<li>关键教训: 对TSMOM信号做基于IC的品种过滤是有害的——动量是广谱因子，强制过滤会丢失多样化收益</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.26, 通过)</strong>: 移除IC gate，改为质量加权信号（weight by q值而非等权平均），保留4窗口q平均。增加E=0.45宽松过滤变体。</p>\n<ul><li>关键转折: (1) 质量加权 vs 等权方向：让高质量回看期有更大影响力；(2) 宽松过滤(E=0.45, z_cut=0.13)效果最好——只过滤极弱信号，保留大部分交易机会；(3) 截面标准化(_cs)在此因子上提升显著（0.84→1.26），说明因子的截面离散度本身含信息</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（57个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 5天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 原报告基于日内小时级数据，日频适配损失了频率维度的独立交易机会\n<p>- 换手率偏高(7.55)但因signal filtering已大幅降低无效交易 - 2017和2022-2023年Sharpe偏低，趋势弱势期信号质量下降 - 最优变体为_cs（截面标准化），说明因子本身的绝对值不够稳定</p>\n<ul><li><strong>与因子库关系</strong>: 与现有动量类因子(如 xinye TSRM, corr=0.528 R1→降至0.343 R3)差异化明显，自适应选择机制是核心区分点</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>EWMA_HL</code></td><td><code>21</code></td><td>conditional vol half-life</td></tr><tr><td><code>RANKING_WINDOWS</code></td><td><code>[42, 63, 126, 252]</code></td><td>quality metric windows</td></tr><tr><td><code>E_VAL</code></td><td><code>0.45</code></td><td>signal magnitude filter</td></tr><tr><td><code>Z_CUT</code></td><td><code>0.13</code></td><td>z-score threshold (from e_map[0.45])</td></tr><tr><td><code>TOP_K</code></td><td><code>3</code></td><td>top-k horizons for quality weighting</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 5.56s</li>\n</ul>"}